# Project Structure Guide

This repository is a CV site (Jekyll-based) with documentation and developer tooling.

- Main CV content: [README.md](mdc:README.md)
- Developer docs: [README_DEV.md](mdc:README_DEV.md)
- Jekyll configuration: [_config.yml](mdc:_config.yml)
- Assets (images, styles): `assets/`
- Pre-commit configuration: [.pre-commit-config.yaml](mdc:.pre-commit-config.yaml)
- README date check script: [scripts/check_readme_date.sh](mdc:scripts/check_readme_date.sh)

Notes
- Commits should follow Conventional Commits.
- The README must end with a line in the format: `Last updated: Month YYYY` (English locale).
- The pre-commit hook enforces the README date when README.md is modified.